de.tub.pes.syscir.sc_model

Class SCFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tub.pes.syscir.sc_model.SCFunction

  • public class SCFunction
extends java.lang.Object
    represents a SystemC-Function with a name, a list of parameters, a returntype, a list of expressions which represents the body of the function and a lsit of variables which are declared inside the function
    Author:
    Florian
